      "date": "2018-04-04 00:24:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nTests uploaded by AT Release Candidate from trevis-67vm1 for review-ldiskfs received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/93bbbc1a-d7b4-4e1c-a2a9-e16863dd85bb). Ran 5 tests. No failures.",
